40|$|The first long {{wavelength}} pin-HEMT <b>photoreceiver</b> {{grown on}} GaAs has been manufactured using a 0. 3 mu m gate length AlGaAs/ GaAs HEMT process. At a wavelength of 1. 55 mu m the monolithically integrated InGaAs pin photodiode has a responsivity of 0. 40 A/W, and the <b>photoreceiver</b> has a - 3 dB bandwidth of 6. 9 GHz. Clear and open eye diagrams for a 10 Gbit/s 1. 55 mu m. optical data stream have been demonstrated...|$|E
